        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>ublius</ex></expan> Arrius <expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>ubli</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>Ouf</abbr><ex>entina</ex></expan> Rufus <lb n="3"/>Magia <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>uci</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilia</ex></expan> Rufa <lb n="4"/>mater fecit <lb n="5"/>de suo
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Gens Arria ist bereits in Canusium bekannt: CIL IX 352; AE 1945, 81; nomen gentile Magius erscheint zum 1. Mal in dieser Stadt.</p>
            </div>
